# playbackRate

**Instance Property**

The chosen playback rate for the command event.

## Declaration

```swift
var playbackRate: Float { get }
```

## Discussion

The `playbackRate` property is equal to a value stored in the [doc://com.apple.mediaplayer/documentation/MediaPlayer/MPChangePlaybackRateCommand/supportedPlaybackRates] array.
